Provenance: all behavioural data in ./data are aggregated derivatives of the
public Google BigQuery dataset `bigquery-public-data.crypto_bitcoin`, produced
by the queries documented in the paper's Supplementary Material (Section S4).
The two price series are daily BTC/USD closes from CoinMarketCap and Bitstamp,
redistributed here in aggregated daily form for reproduction purposes.
